achievement.title: Keystone Master
achievement.description: Complete a Level 15 or higher Mythic dungeon within the time limit.

achievement.title: Raiding with Leashes IV: Wrath of the Lick King
achievement.description: Collect all of the battle pets listed below from Ulduar, Trial of the Crusader, and Icecrown Citadel.

achievement.title: Protector of the Argussian Reach
achievement.description: Earn Exalted status with the Argussian Reach.

achievement.title: Crucible's Promise
achievement.description: Fully unlock the power of the Netherlight Crucible on one of your artifact weapons.

criteria.description: Require Now You're Cooking With Netherlight

achievement.title: Severed Ties
achievement.description: Defeat two Risen Ghouls during Echo of Sylvanas' Calling of the Highborne phase, then defeat the Echo of Sylvanas in End Time on Heroic Difficulty.

achievement.title: Seat of the Pantheon
achievement.description: Defeat the following bosses in the depths of Antorus, the Burning Throne.

achievement.title: Hope's End
achievement.description: Defeat the following bosses in the depths of Antorus, the Burning Throne.

achievement.title: Forbidden Descent
achievement.description: Defeat the following bosses on the second island of Antorus, the Burning Throne.

achievement.title: Light's Breach
achievement.description: Defeat the following bosses at the entrance to Antorus, the Burning Throne.

achievement.title: Ahead of the Curve: Kil'jaeden
achievement.description: Defeat Kil'jaeden in Tomb of Sargeras on Heroic difficulty or higher, before the opening of Antorus, the Burning Throne.

achievement.title: Sharing is Caring
achievement.description: Pass one of every dish at a Bountiful Table.

achievement.title: From Hell's Heart I Stab at Thee
achievement.description: Defeat the Whale Shark in Vashj'ir (despite or perhaps because of the fact that he drops no loot).

achievement.title: WoW's 13th Anniversary
achievement.description: Logged in during WoW's 13th Anniversary.

achievement.title: Loken kills (Heroic Halls of Lightning)
achievement.description: Loken kills (Heroic Halls of Lightning)

achievement.title: 50 Exalted Reputations
achievement.description: Raise 50 reputations to Exalted.

achievement.title: Officer of the Light
achievement.description: Earn Exalted status with the Army of the Light.

achievement.title: Heroic: Sha of Fear
achievement.description: Defeat the Sha of Fear in Terrace of Endless Spring on Heroic difficulty.

achievement.title: The Mind-Killer
achievement.description: Defeat the Sha of Fear in Terrace of Endless Spring on Normal or Heroic difficulty without any raid members being feared by Dread Spray or Breath of Fear.

achievement.title: Heroic: Lei Shi
achievement.description: Defeat Lei Shi in Terrace of Endless Spring on Heroic difficulty.

achievement.title: Heroic: Protectors of the Endless
achievement.description: Defeat the Protectors of the Endless in Terrace of Endless Spring on Heroic difficulty.

achievement.title: Heroic: Tsulong
achievement.description: Defeat Tsulong in Terrace of Endless Spring on Heroic difficulty.

achievement.title: Who's Got Two Green Thumbs?
achievement.description: Win the Tsulong encounter while keeping the Enchanted Plant alive.

achievement.title: Cage Match
achievement.description: Defeat the Council of Elders in Throne of Thunder on Normal or Heroic difficulty without any creature leaving the center rings.

criteria.description: No creature has left the center ring.

achievement.title: Invasion Obliteration
achievement.description: Defeat each of the following Legion Generals by completing each of the Greater Invasion Point scenarios.

achievement.title: Envision Invasion Eradication
achievement.description: Slay each of the demonic commanders that can control the Invasion Points.

achievement.title: Heroic: Amber-Shaper Un'sok
achievement.description: Defeat Amber-Shaper Un'sok in Heart of Fear on Heroic difficulty.

achievement.title: Heroic: Grand Empress Shek'zeer
achievement.description: Defeat Grand Empress Shek'zeer in Heart of Fear on Heroic difficulty.

achievement.title: Less Than Three
achievement.description: Defeat Wind Lord Mel'jarak without crowd-controlling more than 2 of his swarm at once on Normal or Heroic difficulty in Heart of Fear.

achievement.title: Heroic: Wind Lord Mel'jarak
achievement.description: Defeat Wind Lord Mel'jarak in Heart of Fear on Heroic difficulty.

achievement.title: Heroic: Garalon
achievement.description: Defeat Garalon in Heart of Fear on Heroic difficulty.

achievement.title: Heroic: Blade Lord Ta'yak
achievement.description: Defeat Blade Lord Ta'yak in Heart of Fear on Heroic difficulty.

achievement.title: Heroic: Imperial Vizier Zor'lok
achievement.description: Defeat Imperial Vizier Zor'lok in Heart of Fear on Heroic difficulty.

achievement.title: Heroic: Will of the Emperor
achievement.description: Defeat the Will of the Emperor in Mogu'shan Vaults on Heroic difficulty.
achievement.reward: Title Reward: Delver of the Vaults

achievement.title: 1000 Daily Quests Completed
achievement.description: Complete 1000 daily quests.

achievement.description: Defeat Ymiron after defiantly striking down 6 Risen Warriors in Maw of Souls on Mythic difficulty.
